This is a Cursor-specific overlay. **Canonical source: [`rules/core/styling.md`](https://github.com/commerce-atoms/agents/blob/main/kit/rules/core/styling.md).**

## Rules

- CSS modules MUST be colocated with their components / views (same directory).
- CSS module filenames MUST be lowercase / kebab-case (`button.module.css`, `product-card.module.css`).
- Global styles MUST live in `app/styles/`.
- NO `styles/` subfolders — keep flat.
- Prefer named CSS variables (tokens) over hardcoded values.
